French practitioners qualification ValueSet

A code classifying the qualification of the practitioner (Degree/License/Certificate).

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include the codes as defined in https://mos.esante.gouv.fr/NOS/TRE_R48-DiplomeEtatFrancais/FHIR/TRE-R48-DiplomeEtatFrancais
  • Include the codes as defined in https://mos.esante.gouv.fr/NOS/TRE_R47-CommissionQualification/FHIR/TRE-R47-CommissionQualification
  • Include the codes as defined in https://mos.esante.gouv.fr/NOS/TRE_R49-DiplomeEtudeSpecialisee/FHIR/TRE-R49-DiplomeEtudeSpecialisee
  • Include the codes as defined in https://mos.esante.gouv.fr/NOS/TRE_R50-DESCGroupe1Diplome/FHIR/TRE-R50-DESCGroupe1Diplome
  • Include the codes as defined in https://mos.esante.gouv.fr/NOS/TRE_R51-DESCGroupe2Diplome/FHIR/TRE-R51-DESCGroupe2Diplome
  • Include the codes as defined in https://mos.esante.gouv.fr/NOS/TRE_R53-DiplomePaysEEE/FHIR/TRE-R53-DiplomePaysEEE
  • Include the codes as defined in https://mos.esante.gouv.fr/NOS/TRE_R54-DiplomeUniversiteInterUniversitaire/FHIR/TRE-R54-DiplomeUniversiteInterUniversitaire
  • Include the codes as defined in https://mos.esante.gouv.fr/NOS/TRE_R55-CertificatEtudeSpeciale/FHIR/TRE-R55-CertificatEtudeSpeciale
  • Include the codes as defined in https://mos.esante.gouv.fr/NOS/TRE_R56-Attestation/FHIR/TRE-R56-Attestation
  • Include the codes as defined in https://mos.esante.gouv.fr/NOS/TRE_R52-CapaciteDiplome/FHIR/TRE-R52-CapaciteDiplome
  • Include the codes as defined in https://mos.esante.gouv.fr/NOS/TRE_R58-AutreTypeDiplome/FHIR/TRE-R58-AutreTypeDiplome
  • Include the codes as defined in https://mos.esante.gouv.fr/NOS/TRE_R36-AutreDiplomeObtenu/FHIR/TRE-R36-AutreDiplomeObtenu
  • Include the codes as defined in https://mos.esante.gouv.fr/NOS/TRE_R226-Dip2iemeCycleNQ/FHIR/TRE-R226-Dip2iemeCycleNQ
